      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont even know why i'm still doing this. the lab results came back today and it's just... over. all the years, the funding, the missed sleep... it was all for nothing. i feel like there's nothing left of me outside of this research and now that it's gone, i'm just empty. i'm just so incredibly tired of trying to fix things that are fundamentally broken.",
