      "content": "therapists and crisis lines just feel like more work. more talking, more trying to \"fix\" something that feels fundamentally broken. i'm just so done with the struggle. i look at people who seem to have it figured out and i just feel so much envy because they aren't fighting this every single second. i just want a way to actually find some stillness. to just... stop the fight and finally be at rest.",
